I went on a wild shopping spree through Temu's weirdest tech offerings and boy did I find some gems! From a sketchy "bird watching" device to a vibrating exercise platform, this haul got progressively more bizarre. The highlight might be the streetlight that wasn't quite as advertised - or maybe the eye moisturizing goggles that actually kind of worked?
